<plot>Future Summit: Virtual Worlds examines computer and Internet technology and how it is blurring the lines between reality and imagination. From breathtaking vistas on the movie screen, heart-pounding action in on-line games, to the increasing popularity of on-line social networking, the hour long program shows how these technological developments are shaping our communities and the lives of our children.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?089739</url></doc>
